CatDescriptText: This church building is currently owned by Greater Pittsburgh Gospel Deliverance Center.  They purchased the structure in 1976.
TitMainTitle: Stone church with rounded apse and sign reading "For Sale, Arnheim & Neely" at corner of South Pacific and Friendship Avenues
